---
title: Chermoula Chickpea, Halloumi & Pumpkin Buddha Bowl with Zingy Radish Slaw & Garlic Dip
description: This nourishing bowl will leave you feeling satisfied and energised in equal measure. Between crunchy cabbage, roasted pumpkin and tasty chickpeas, every bite is a delight. Our favourite flourish is the rich garlic dip dolloped on top.

